Name: Description
Fleet-class: The component of the operating model that controls fishing dynamics

Name: Function call
Fleet-class: Objects can be created by calls of the form new('Fleet')

Name: Name
Fleet-class: Name of the Fleet object

Name: nyears
Fleet-class: The number of years for the historical simulation

Name: Spat_targ
Fleet-class: Distribution of fishing in relation to spatial biomass: F is proportional to B^Spat_targ (uniform distribution)

Name: Esd
Fleet-class: Inter-annual variability in fishing mortality rate

Name: EffYears
Fleet-class: Vector of verticies, years at which to simulate varying relative effort

Name: EffLower
Fleet-class: Lower bound on relative effort corresponding to EffYears (uniform distribution)

Name: EffUpper
Fleet-class: Uppper bound on relative effort corresponding to EffYears (uniform distribution)

Name: LFS
Fleet-class: Shortest length that is fully vulnerable to fishing (uniform distribution)

Name: L5
Fleet-class: Shortest length corresponding ot 5 percent vulnerability (uniform distribution)

Name: Vmaxlen
Fleet-class: The vulnerability of the longest (oldest) fish (uniform distribution)

Name: SelYears
Fleet-class: Vector of verticies, index for years at which historical selectivity pattern changed. If left empty, historical selectivity is constant

Name: AbsSelYears
Fleet-class: Optional values for SelYears, used for plotting only. Must be of same length as SelYears

Name: L5Lower
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying lower limits of L5 (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: L5Upper
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying upper limits of L5 (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: LFSLower
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying lower limits of LFS (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: LFSUpper
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying upper limits of LFS (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: VmaxLower
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying lower limits of Vmaxlen (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: VmaxUpper
Fleet-class: Optional vector of values of length SelYears, specifiying upper limits of Vmaxlen (use  ChooseSelect  function to set these)

Name: qinc
Fleet-class: Average percentage change in fishing efficiency (uniform distribution)(applicable only to forward projection and input controls)

Name: qcv
Fleet-class: Inter-annual variability in fishing efficiency (uniform distribution)(applicable only to forward projection and input controls)

Name: isRel
Fleet-class: Are the selectivity parameters relative to size-of-maturity? TRUE or FALSE

Name: CurrentYr
Fleet-class: The current calendar year (final year) of the historical simulations (e.g. 2011)
